stries from  to  until its merger with lafarge for gbp£ billion in cash he served as the chief executive officer of invensys from  to  he was a partner of star capital partners from  to  he also served as the chairman of network rail haythornthwaite has served as the chairman of mastercard since may  he has also served as the chairman of centrica since january  haythornthwaite served on the boards of directors of the imperial chemical industries lafarge premier oil and land securities philanthropyedit haythornthwaite served as the chairman of the board of governors of the southbank centre for seven years standing down in january  he also serves as member of the board of the world wide web foundation he is a fellow of the royal society of arts personal lifeedit he was nicknamed slick rick in a single newspaper piece but the sobriquet has never been used since referencesedit  centrica plc companies house retrieved  october    a b c d e f g h i j board of directors mastercard retrieved october     company overview of star capital partners limited richard n haythornthwaite bloomberg business retrieved october     richard haythornthwaite profile at world economic forum weforumorg retrieved  october    a b c governance centrica retrieved october     a b c d kavanagh michael october   centrica appoints rick haythornthwaite as chairman financial times retrieved october     a b macalister terry october   exnetwork rail boss to head centrica the guardian retrieved october     board of governors southbank centre retrieved october     our board world wide web foundation retrieved october     richard haythornthwaite world economic forum retrieved october     pfeifer sylvia february   third time lucky for slick rick the daily telegraph retrieved october    retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitlerichardhaythornthwaiteoldid categories  birthsliving peoplealumni of the queens college oxfordmit sloan fellowsmit sloan school of management alumnibritish business executivesbrit